snippet.title: Lost Records: Bloom and Rage - Reveal Trailer | Game Awards 2023
snippet.description:
From Don't Nod, the developers of Life is Strange, comes Lost Records: Bloom and Rage, a new narrative adventure game releasing in late 2024. Check out the reveal trailer, shown at The Game Awards 2023. 

#ign #gaming #thegameawards #dontnod
